Create new folder on desktop - my_website
Inside new folder, create static and templates folders
create server.py file
Using downloaded template - store index.html in templates and .css, .js, assets, .ico, images in static
Make sure to check all path in index.html are correctly change by adding static in the path

cd Desktop
python -m venv my_website
. my_website/bin/activate
pip install Flask
pip install --upgrade pip
cd my_website
export FLASK_ENV=development
export FLASK_APP=server.py
python -m flask run

